subject: Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Kevin Craddock of the United States won the 60-meter hurdles, topping the Olympic champion Dayron Robles of Cuba at an indoor meet in Düsseldorf, Germany.
snippet: Kevin Craddock of the United States won the 60-meter hurdles, topping the Olympic champion Dayron Robles of Cuba at an indoor meet in Düsseldorf, Germany.
